:PC.
The paragraph continuation tag signals the
start of a paragraph continuation.
A paragraph continuation tag will be necessary when another
basic document element, such as an example, is placed
in the middle of a paragraph.
Most layouts do not indent the first line of a paragraph continuation.
:p.The tag may be used wherever a basic document element is
permitted.
